{"tid":1799790,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「飛雲」近距離接近仇B 嘅機會","createTime":"2019-12-27T08:17:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-27T16:04:15.000Z","uid":4574,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"47e74e8df39b30b5e64978c7c2177a644aec318d","tid":1799790,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T08:17:49.000Z","msg":"阿欣請人(全職）<br />\n<br />\n如果你有興趣和阿欣一齊係城市花園工作😆為社區服務，請將履歷連同要求待遇，電郵至jocelynrecruitment2020@gmail.com申請處理需時，請耐心等待🙏🏻<br />\n<br />\n申請人所提供的資料將予以保密及只作招聘有關職位用途。<br />\n<br />\n因反送中運動而被捕、檢控或定罪者不拘!<br />\n───────────────────────<br />\n- 全職（行政及個案跟進）<br />\n- 全職（出版及設計）<br />\n<br />\n工作時間：<br />\n- 每周工作44小時（全職）<br />\n<br />\n- 有時需外勤、輪值及假日工作<br />\n<br />\n工作範圍：<br />\n- 辦事處日常運作<br />\n<br />\n- 處理區議會事務及社區聯絡<br />\n<br />\n- 策劃社區項目（如街站、居民會議及地區活動）<br />\n<br />\n- 跟進居民個案<br />\n<br />\n- 製作地區文宣<br />\n<br />\n職位要求：<br />\n- 良好溝通技巧（懂方言更佳）、中英文書寫能力<br />\n<br />\n- 熟悉電腦操作、懂中文打字<br />\n<br />\n- 對社區服務有興趣、能獨立工作、具團體精神、有責任感、積極主動<br />\n<br />\n- 能運用 Photoshop 及多媒體製作軟件，有媒體經驗更佳（如校園媒體、學生報）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uESWbG8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuESWbG8.jpg&h=b879f958&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f35c4296d75b750f78bf5765ce0f511c179a4e5","tid":1799790,"uid":7854,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T08:18:39.000Z","msg":"近距離聞黑絲腳味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26eb248139cf29dd19f7692e307dbd5adc0ee355","tid":1799790,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T08:21:17.000Z","msg":"張相影到好怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8ed652a09e8d7cccdfb304ec9a2d52a281d007e","tid":1799790,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T14:30:06.000Z","msg":"有調教feel"},{"pid":"6d6b550a5197fc700900f81245a9ba515768f6aa","tid":17